ji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:58:41.000Z","msg":"咁又好似多咗哈哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"065fd845349b06c0bfde1eb09f1d46516cdb73cd","tid":1630312,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:58:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"d0a42a9f6a8f3d5753c13f7a674b9ec4b49daf69","tid":1630312,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:59:39.000Z","msg":"十月十，爆買日！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1631347/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1631347/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n和理非時間！"},{"pid":"cc35205453d65feaee3e9b7b6bb9165a88c26514","tid":1630312,"uid":169391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:00:26.000Z","msg":"不如泥個總結先，暫時有<br />\n1. 爆買黃店<br />\n2. 感謝美國/世界旗仔燈仔流水式/個人式集會<br />\n3. 五區在政府建築物行一圈+貼文宣<br />\n4. 唱歌/放映會<br />\n<br />\n有冇邊個特別想做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae5faea98dd5a39959a15bc899a872b3f237f75f","tid":1630312,"uid":169391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0acd83732ab662c8d17aeb8dee6d1d55bfc8213e","tid":1630312,"uid":296109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6f769e0ac37a11fd9be67e322d7c1ee8e4f8528","tid":1630312,"uid":169391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33e7ac4c7ca8db9379872c04a74565c8f336a277","tid":1630312,"uid":296109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:16:04.000Z","msg":"針對<spa